
= cutagem

by cho45 <cho45@lowreal.net>

== Description

cutagem (Cut a Gem) is yet another executable of creating gem skelton.

== Installation

=== Archive Installation

	rake install

=== Gem Installation

	gem install cutagem

=== Subversion Repository

Hosted by CodeRepos[http://coderepos.org/share/browser/lang/ruby/cutagem]

	svn co http://svn.coderepos.org/share/lang/ruby/cutagem/


== Usage

	$ cutagem gemname
	lib/gemname

	$ cutagem module-test
	lib/module/test

Select templates interactively. (-s, --select option)

	$ cutagem -s module-test
	lib/module/test

== Customization

+cutagem+ read ~/.cutagem/template to use custom template as it.

